  "id": "RAW_4ea0cec1",
  "title": "对话吴嘉：打通阿里生态之后，千问还要做什么？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&mid=2247624229&idx=1&sn=e0e174e560cb3fc6111d8588a180ae7a",
  "date": "2026-01-16 03:46:00",
  "author": "硅星人Pro",
  "siteName": "硅星人Pro",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 30px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;background:none;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"562\" data-backw=\"562\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jopKOlhibRBI3no59J0Q9GDxxzpkVYm3sMib1AkRT99ibOhFBdrKIAMTZxl4WUOqPkMP5vFKGbW1gWv27ka42hHBw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100140577\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b7702c02&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjopKOlhibRBI3no59J0Q9GDxxzpkVYm3sMib1AkRT99ibOhFBdrKIAMTZxl4WUOqPkMP5vFKGbW1gWv27ka42hHBw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 15px 0px 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-size: 13px;line-height: 21px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者</span><i style=\"letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">｜</span></i><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">Yoky</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><span leaf=\"\">邮箱</span><i style=\"letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">｜</span></i><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">yokyliu@pingwest.com</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">千问对自己挺狠的，或者说阿里对自己挺狠的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">用一个千问，把过去二十年的阿里，变成了一个AI Agent。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">1月15日，千问App宣布全面接入淘宝、支付宝、淘宝闪购、飞猪、高德等</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">基本上</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">阿里生态</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">中的关键</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">的所有</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">业务，上线超400项AI办事功能，在全球首次实现点外卖、买东西、订机票等AI购物能力，向所有用户开放。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">基本上你可以用一个千问，调用整个阿里。阿里巴巴副总裁、千问C端事业群总裁吴嘉进一步透露：“千问计划在半年内打通整个阿里生态，并将持续规划引入第三方伙伴。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这使得千问构建的能力壁垒，在全球范围内几乎难以复制：OpenAI没有电商，谷歌没有支付，亚马逊没有自研的顶尖模型。它们的Agent能聊天、能搜索、能写代码，却难以深入真正的交易闭环。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">或许</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">大部分</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">人</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">还没有意识到，</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">千问此次</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">升级远非一次交互方式的变革，它标志着阿里在内部达成了前所未有的协同与统一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">以此为起点，阿里已经进入全面拥抱AI的“战时”状态。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">实测：千问如何把阿里变成一个Agent？</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了实测千问的边界，我给了它一个相当复杂的任务，可不是点个外卖那么简单：帮我制定北京到西藏七天的旅行计划，1月16日～1月23日，预算2w，一个人。并帮我整理好御寒所需要的装备列表，选购加入淘宝购物车。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是一个并行任务，需要调用搜索、高德、飞猪、淘宝等多个APP，下面是完整的执行过程（只加速不剪辑），在执行的过程中，可以看出很多千问的思路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">整个任务千问用了7分钟，它头脑清楚，几乎没有多余的动作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一步千问先去搜了“1月西藏旅游注意事项”“冬季西藏穿什么”“拉萨到纳木错怎么走”这类基础信息。它在建立对这个任务的基本认知：冬天去西藏冷不冷、会不会有高原反应、哪些景点开放、大概的行程怎么安排。这一步像是一个人在做攻略前先搜一圈别人的游记。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">有了基本概念之后，千问开始查具体的距离和路线。它在用高德把景点之间的空间关系搞清楚，这样才能把行程排得合理，不会让你上午在东边下午跑到一百公里外的西边。然后通过调用飞猪，去查1月16日北京到拉萨的机票，查1月23日拉萨回北京的机票，查拉萨市区的酒店。这一步是在确认真实的价格和库存，推荐用户选择具体哪个航班几点起飞多少钱还有没有票。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">在生成结果时，千问用Python</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">写了一段代码，用来计算预算分配并生成攻略。所有信息汇总，输出一份完整的七日行程单：每天去哪、住哪、怎么走、花多少钱，外加一份御寒装备清单。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">有一个细节很关键：最终生成的攻略里，每一个环节都可以直接点击购票和预订，不用跳转到飞猪，不用跳转到高德，全在千问里完成。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就是“调用”和“连接”的区别。它不是一个超级入口去连接十几个APP，它是一个Agent直接调度十几个APP的能力。那些APP变成了千问的手和脚，而不是千问引流的目的地。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">当然，目前的千问也存在着一些问题。比如我明确要求了“选购加入淘宝购物车”，它没有执行。装备清单列出来了，但只是文字，没有真的帮我加进购物车。推测原因是千问目前一次只能完成一个主任务，“规划行程”和“加购物车”被它理解成了两件事，它做完第一件就停了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">但这并不是能力缺失，更像是一个对于复杂需求理解层级的问题。</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">千问已经能够调度阿里的多</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">项</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">个</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">服务</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">来</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">完成复杂任务，这件事本身成立了。今天</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">呈现出来</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">展示</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">的，</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">是它</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">能力的下限，上限是什么样，取决于模型对人的需求能理解到多深。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">先打通阿里，然后连接一切</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">时至今日我们早已经明白，AI注定要连接一切，问题在于连接谁</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">？</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">怎么连接</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">？</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI在这方面遇到了麻烦。即便它拥有世界上顶尖的闭源模型，但没有互联网生态的它只能去连接别人。亚马逊封禁了ChatGPT的访问，而这原本是OpenAI一项重要的商业计划，让AI直接在电商网站上帮用户下单以赚取成交费用。没有自己的电商、没有自己的支付、没有自己的本地生活，OpenAI的模型能力再强，也得看别人脸色。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这背后其实是整个互联网格局的结构性问题：</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">谷歌有搜索、有地图、有邮箱，但没有电商，没有支付</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">，做不到真正的闭环</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">而</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">亚马逊有电商、有支付，但没有</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">基础</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">模型</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。互联网巨头们各有各的长板，也各有各的缺口</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">，</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">很少有人能同时握住“模型+场景+交易”的完整链条</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">可</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">阿里的位置不一样。它几乎是唯一一个同时拥有全球范围内的顶尖模型和完整生态的企业，淘宝、支付宝、飞猪、高德、饿了么、优酷、1688、闲鱼</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">等等</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">，千问调用它们，不需要谈判，不需要分成，不需要担心哪天被封禁。</span></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5253333333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"750\" height=\"634\" style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;width:100%;display:block;letter-spacing:inherit;\" width=\"1206\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"295\" data-imgfileid=\"100140561\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b4d567bc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmb