n-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前，业内普遍认为：</span></span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">模型能力和智能化水平是</span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">入场券</span></span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">门槛</span></span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">，它们</span></span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">决定Agent的下限，但生态的完整性和互通性</span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">，才</span></span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">决定了Agent的</span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">天花板</span></span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">边界</span></span></span></b><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">。这一轮竞赛，阿里手里的牌很齐。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过，这只是个起点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">吴嘉告诉硅星人，千问事业群与其他业务部门正在紧密配合，双方合作成立了虚拟项目组。目前70%的精力集中在技术侧的打通，每个功能采取了不同的方式，有的是内部接口直连，有的走A2A协议，有的环节用GUI去理解内容。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术方向的打通将在半年之内完成。接下来是更深一层的整合：业务的打通、运营的打通。比如外卖的进度卡是否要在千问中实时显示？用户在千问下的打车订单，高德那边如何同步处理？这次新功能上线，千问和淘宝闪购一起为用户提供了一定的大额红包用于拉新，后续内部也会作为一个整体持续对外运营。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">“无论是在千问还是在淘宝、淘宝闪购的APP下单，都是在阿里体系里，对我们来说是一样的。”吴嘉说道。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这句话背后的意思是：用户从哪个门进来不重要，重要的是进来之后，整个阿里都在为他服务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">打通内部，对于千问而言，也只是一次探索和验证。阿里生态再大，也不可能覆盖所有场景。如果千问只能调用阿里自己的服务，它的能力边界就被框死了。通过跑通阿里来跑通技术、验证模式、打磨体验。一旦这个样本成立，下一步就是把同样的能力开放给外部。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><b style=\"font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">吴嘉透露，接下来千问会开放更多第三方应用接入，和合作伙伴一起共创更大的Agent生态。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这意味着千问的野心不止于“阿里的Agent”，而是想成为“所有服务的Agent”。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深入分析了阿里千问如何通过深度整合阿里生态，构建独一无二的 AI Agent，实现从信息查询到复杂交易闭环的全链路服务，并展望了其未来开放第三方接入的宏伟愿景。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深入分析了阿里千问如何通过深度整合阿里生态，构建独一无二的 AI Agent，实现从信息查询到复杂交易闭环的全链路服务，并展望了其未来开放第三方接入的宏伟愿景。",
  "summary": "文章围绕阿里千问 App 全面接入淘宝、支付宝、高德等阿里核心业务，上线 400 余项 AI 办事功能展开。通过作者亲身实测复杂旅行规划任务，展示了千问作为 AI Agent，如何直接调度阿里生态内的多个应用能力，而非简单跳转链接，实现从信息搜索、路径规划到机票酒店预订的无缝体验。文章强调，阿里通过“模型+场景+交易”的完整链条，构建了全球范围内 OpenAI、谷歌、亚马逊等巨头难以复制的能力壁垒。同时，文中也指出了当前千问在处理多任务需求时的局限性。未来，千问不仅要完成阿里内部的技术与业务整合，更计划开放第三方应用接入，旨在成为连接所有服务的 Agent。",
  "mainPoints": [
